"    Potential symptoms and signs of anaphylaxis during pregnancy",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 424px; height: 536px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
