"      Tang WW, Kaptein EM, Feinstein EI, Massry SG. Hyponatremia in hospitalized patients with the acquired immunodeficiency syndrome (AIDS) and the AIDS-related complex. Am J Med 1993; 94:169.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?38/26/39332/abstract/4\">",
"      Kalin MF, Poretsky L, Seres DS, Zumoff B. Hyporeninemic hypoaldosteronism associated with acquired immune deficiency syndrome. Am J Med 1987; 82:1035.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?38/26/39332/abstract/5\">",
"      Guy RJ, Turberg Y, Davidson RN, et al. Mineralocorticoid deficiency in HIV infection. BMJ 1989; 298:496.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
